IF gs_detlevel_3D_m=0 then END IF GLOB_CONTEXT>20 and GLOB_CONTEXT<40 THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m=1

!! Height Editing unID=1 hotspot a, b, 0, unID, zzyzx, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot a, b, -1, unID, zzyzx, 3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot a, b, zzyzx, unID, zzyzx, 2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot 0, b, 0, unID, zzyzx, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, b, -1, unID, zzyzx, 3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, b, zzyzx, unID, zzyzx, 2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot a, 0, 0, unID, zzyzx, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot a, 0, -1, unID, zzyzx, 3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot a, 0, zzyzx, unID, zzyzx, 2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot 0, 0, 0, unID, zzyzx, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, -1, unID, zzyzx, 3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, zzyzx, unID, zzyzx, 2 : unID=unID+1
!! Lower Door Height Editing
hotspot 0, 0, 0, unID, low_door_h, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, 0-1, unID, low_door_h, 3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, 0+low_door_h, unID, low_door_h, 2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot a, 0, 0, unID, low_door_h, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot a, 0, 0-1, unID, low_door_h, 3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot a, 0, 0+low_door_h, unID, low_door_h, 2 : unID=unID+1
PEN gs_cont_pen MATERIAL gs_cabinet_mat
!!!!!****************************************** CALL GENERAL BASE CABINET
IF UpCabinet THEN !! Upper Cabinet temp_drawer_h=up_door_h-0.02 temp_door_h=low_door_h-toe_h ELSE temp_drawer_h=0 temp_door_h=ZZYZX-toe_h ENDIF
IF UpCabinet THEN ADD 0.02,fr_th1,low_door_h-0.01 MATERIAL gs_ShelfMat PRISM_ 5,0.02, 0,0,15, a-0.02*2,0,15, a-0.02*2,b-0.02-fr_th1,15, 0,b-0.02-fr_th1,15, 0,0,-1 DEL 1 ENDIF
unID=100 basecab_unID=unID CALL "fa_gen_basecabinet" PARAMETERS a=a, b=b, zzyzx=zzyzx, gs_detlevel_3D_m=gs_detlevel_3D_m, dob_face=dob_face, count_th=count_th, front_cab=front_cab, rear_cab=rear_cab, left_cab=left_cab, right_cab=right_cab, toe_h=toe_h, side_vis_m=side_vis_m+1, sink=sink, shelf_num=shelf_num, gs_ShelfMat=gs_ShelfMat, gs_cont_pen=gs_cont_pen, gs_shadow=gs_shadow, toe_mat=toe_mat, gs_cabinet_mat=gs_cabinet_mat, drawer_h=temp_drawer_h, toe_d = toe_d,gs_toe_type_m=gs_toe_type_m,fr_th1=fr_th1, basecab_unID=basecab_unID, returned_parameters basecab_unID unID = basecab_unID
!!!!!****************************************** CALL DOOR PANEL door_w=(a-left_cab-right_cab)/2 if low_door then ADD left_cab,front_cab+fr_th1,toe_h GOSUB "lower door" !*** LOWER LEFT DOOR ADDx a-left_cab-right_cab mulx -1 GOSUB "lower door" !*** LOWER RIGHT DOOR del 1 DEL 2 endif
if up_door and UpCabinet then ADD left_cab,front_cab+fr_th1,low_door_h
if gs_knob_p_m=0 then ! vertical if gs_knob_type_m=4 then knob_pl_y_up=knob_pl_y_up+0.113 if gs_knob_type_m>4 then knob_pl_y_up=knob_pl_y_up+0.1 endif GOSUB "upper door" !*** UPPER LEFT DOOR ADDx a-left_cab-right_cab mulx -1 GOSUB "upper door" !*** UPPER RIGHT DOOR del 1 DEL 2 endif
!!!!!****************************************** CALL END PANELS
IF rear_panel and dob_face = 0 then door_w=(a-left_cab-right_cab)/2: door_h=ZZYZX-toe_h-count_th ADD door_w+left_cab,b-rear_cab,toe_h ROTZ 180 GOSUB "end panel" ADDX -door_w GOSUB "end panel" DEL 3 ENDIF
IF left_panel then door_w=b-fr_th1-rear_cab: door_h=ZZYZX-toe_h-count_th !*** LEFT END PANEL ADD left_cab,door_w+fr_th1,toe_h ROTZ -90 GOSUB "end panel" DEL 2 ENDIF
IF right_panel then door_w=b-fr_th1-rear_cab: door_h=ZZYZX-toe_h-count_th ADD a-right_cab,fr_th1,toe_h ROTZ 90 GOSUB "end panel" DEL 2 ENDIF
END
!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! *** RETURN *** !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
! ============================================================================== "lower door":
cabdoortyp_unID=unID
CALL "fa_cabdoortyp" PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D_m=gs_detlevel_3D_m,gs_full_edit=gs_full_edit, door_w=door_w, door_h=temp_door_h, gs_door_type_m=gs_door_type_m,gs_shadow=gs_shadow, doorframe_w=doorframe_w, gs_cont_pen=gs_cont_pen, doorglas_mat=doorglas_mat, gs_bevel=gs_bevel, vert_gnum=vert_gnum, hor_gnum=hor_gnum,fr_th1=fr_th1, doorframe_mat=doorframe_mat, door_ang=door_ang,gs_cust_p=gs_cust_p, gs_knob_type_m=gs_knob_type_m,gs_knob_p_m=gs_knob_p_m,knob_size=knob_size, knob_pl_x=knob_pl_x,knob_pl_y=knob_pl_y, gs_knob_mat=gs_knob_mat, cabdoortyp_unID=cabdoortyp_unID, gs_cust_knob = gs_cust_knob, gs_customHandleLength = gs_customHandleLength, gs_customHandleHeight = gs_customHandleHeight, gs_customHandleDepth = gs_customHandleDepth, returned_parameters cabdoortyp_unID
unID = cabdoortyp_unID
RETURN

cabdoortyp_unID=unID
CALL "fa_cabdoortyp" PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D_m=gs_detlevel_3D_m,gs_full_edit=gs_full_edit, door_w=door_w, door_h=up_door_h, gs_door_type_m=gs_door_type_m,gs_shadow=gs_shadow, doorframe_w=doorframe_w, gs_cont_pen=gs_cont_pen, doorglas_mat=doorglas_mat, vert_gnum=vert_gnum2, hor_gnum=hor_gnum2,fr_th1=fr_th1, doorframe_mat=doorframe_mat, door_ang=door_ang, gs_cust_p=gs_cust_p, UpperKnob=1,gs_bevel=gs_bevel, gs_knob_type_m=gs_knob_type_m,gs_knob_p_m=gs_knob_p_m,knob_size=knob_size, knob_pl_x_up=knob_pl_x_up,knob_pl_y_up=knob_pl_y_up, gs_knob_mat=gs_knob_mat, cabdoortyp_unID=cabdoortyp_unID, gs_cust_knob = gs_cust_knob, gs_customHandleLength = gs_customHandleLength, gs_customHandleHeight = gs_customHandleHeight, gs_customHandleDepth = gs_customHandleDepth, returned_parameters cabdoortyp_unID
unID = cabdoortyp_unID
RETURN
!!!!!****************************************** END PANELS "end panel": !! on rear panel there is no glas and grilles and knobs!! door_open=0 gs_knob_type_m=0 If end_panel_type=`Стиль 1` then gs_door_type_m=1 If end_panel_type=`Стиль 2` then gs_door_type_m=2 If end_panel_type=`Стиль 4` then gs_door_type_m=11 If end_panel_type=`Стиль 7` then gs_door_type_m=4 If end_panel_type=`Стиль 9` then gs_door_type_m=6 If end_panel_type=`Спец. панель` then gs_door_type_m=10 gs_full_edit=0
cabdoortyp_unID=unID CALL "fa_cabdoortyp" PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D_m=gs_detlevel_3D_m,gs_full_edit=0, door_w=door_w, door_h=temp_door_h, gs_door_type_m=gs_door_type_m,gs_shadow=gs_shadow, doorframe_w=doorframe_w_end, gs_cont_pen=gs_cont_pen, doorglas_mat=doorframe_mat_end, gs_knob_mat=gs_knob_mat, doorframe_mat=doorframe_mat_end, gs_knob_type_m=gs_knob_type_m,knob_pl_y=low_door_h/2, gs_cust_p=gs_cust_p_end,gs_bevel=gs_bevel, cabdoortyp_unID=cabdoortyp_unID, gs_cust_knob = gs_cust_knob, gs_customHandleLength = gs_customHandleLength, gs_customHandleHeight = gs_customHandleHeight, gs_customHandleDepth = gs_customHandleDepth, returned_parameters cabdoortyp_unID
unID = cabdoortyp_unID
IF UpCabinet=1 THEN ADDZ low_door_h-toe_h
cabdoortyp_unID=unID CALL "fa_cabdoortyp" PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D_m=gs_detlevel_3D_m,gs_full_edit=0, door_w=door_w, door_h=up_door_h, gs_door_type_m=gs_door_type_m,gs_shadow=gs_shadow, doorframe_w=doorframe_w_end, gs_cont_pen=gs_cont_pen, doorglas_mat=doorframe_mat_end, gs_knob_mat=gs_knob_mat, doorframe_mat=doorframe_mat_end, gs_knob_type_m=gs_knob_type_m,knob_pl_y=low_door_h/2, gs_cust_p=gs_cust_p_end,gs_bevel=gs_bevel, cabdoortyp_unID=cabdoortyp_unID, gs_cust_knob = gs_cust_knob, gs_customHandleLength = gs_customHandleLength, gs_customHandleHeight = gs_customHandleHeight, gs_customHandleDepth = gs_customHandleDepth, returned_parameters cabdoortyp_unID
unID = cabdoortyp_unID
DEL 1 ENDIF
RETURN
